<BaseLayout sideBarActiveItemID="home">
    <div class="pb-12 mt-12">
        <div class="text-xl py-1">Hey there 👋 I'm</div>
        <div class="text-5xl pt-6 pb-2 font-bold">Tatenda Muvhu</div>
        <div class="text-xl py-4 font-normal mt-4 text-gray-500">Electrical and Computer Engineer • Software Developer
            • AI Enthusiast • MPhil FinTech
        </div>
        <div class="text-justify py-6">
            <p class="">
                <text class="">
                    A skilled and forward-thinking professional in Cape Town, South Africa who possesses a unique blend
                    of critical and innovative thinking that enables me to tackle complex engineering and software
                    problems with ease. With a proven track record of delivering results on time and within budget,
                    I am a fast learner who constantly seeks to enhance my technical expertise and stay abreast with
                    emerging technologies. Whether working independently or as part of a team, I am committed to
                    delivering exceptional results that drive business success.
                </text>
            </p>


            <p class="pt-6">
                <text class="">
                    My passion is good software using industry proven technologies and best practices. From the
                    implementation of customized software solutions to enterprise application development and
                    integration, e-business portals, e-integration, web and mobile application development, I have
                    the right skill set to implement solutions on any platform.
                </text>
            </p>


            <p class="pt-6">
                <text class="">
                    Get in touch and lets discuss your project requirements.
                </text>
            </p>

        </div>
        <div class="mt-12">
            <a class="btn rounded-lg" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tatenda-muvhu" target="_blank"> Let's
                connect!</a>
        </div>
    </div>

